<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="15" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[189,1399,1886,1982]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
This species is represented by two subspecies: nominate, inhabiting the plains of the eastern part of 
<collectingCountry box="[189,354,1921,1947]" name="Turkmenistan" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Turkmenistan</collectingCountry>
, and 
<emphasis box="[415,547,1921,1947]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">binaluduca</emphasis>
subsp. nov. found in the mountainous regions of eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1215,1262,1921,1947]" name="Iran" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Iran</collectingCountry>
and central 
<collectingCountry box="[189,336,1956,1982]" name="Afghanistan" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Afghanistan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
